{"tid":2455858,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"姐姐派吉野家飯比班老野食 ， 唔驚啃死佢哋？","createTime":"2021-03-21T12:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T13:00:19.000Z","uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9929f9d36b566263420390f54c256bc3c7a498c3","tid":2455858,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nNtyZPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNtyZPU.jpg&h=36128fc2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtiSvWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtiSvWz.jpg&h=2182b93f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gfLtOJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgfLtOJf.jpg&h=5ba3333a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dY3jaWA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdY3jaWA.jpg&h=523d22b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【愛心派飯 為長者送暖】<br />\n<br />\n為迎接新民黨十周年，近日敝黨黨友走訪各區派發愛心牛肉飯。繼早前我分別到鰂魚涌及上水等地區後，今天我又去到西灣河區，為長者上門送飯。<br />\n<br />\n我很喜歡這項活動，因為可以親身視察民情，為他們提供最適切的協助。而今天我送飯的對象，主要是年過八十的長者，其中幾戶，更超過九十歲。同行的社區發展主任林梓鴻告訴我，他們一向支持我們的地區工作，即使行動不便，亦在敝黨參加立法會及區議會選舉時，親自前來投票，實在令我十分感動。<br />\n<br />\n而令我印象最深刻，是一對年過九十歲的夫婦。他們不單十分壯健，每天都會在家傭協助下行公園，更難得的是結婚超過七十年，兒孩滿堂，實在令人非常羡慕。<br />\n<br />\n記得上次探訪上水區，居民活在細小且簡陋的劏房內，看得心有忐忑。今次見到各位長者健康長壽，頤養天年，不禁心中一暖。"},{"pid":"9fecb38a12a4d78f8bc76906598dea7332ff9fdb","tid":2455858,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:47:48.000Z","msg":"目的就係咁"},{"pid":"ad6f4dac9b2b2a8f88096dce4430d501236a6fb6","tid":2455858,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:50:12.000Z","msg":"對奶幾大"},{"pid":"ad51418aa5dca335fbaed478ae5db282043ca0fd","tid":2455858,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:52:16.000Z","msg":"吉野姐姐"},{"pid":"caa8f37284f3a01a1600b2923ccbe3e3380415d6","tid":2455858,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:53:40.000Z","msg":"班長者隨時反日反左大半世<br />\n臨老反而要食日本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c33e7d25b0eabf514d762ac18e591bf954febd","tid":2455858,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ad6f4dac9b2b2a8f88096dce4430d501236a6fb6","tid":2455858,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:50:12.000Z","msg":"對奶幾大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kabE9zM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkabE9zM.gif&h=0c69f230&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e515b2f5d8fb0da597f70560809c68267d957e9b","tid":2455858,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"派大日本帝國嘅飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}